{"id": 35, "genre": 1000, "title": "弹幕电影突然火了，你有兴趣看吗？", "description": "从上个星期《秦时明月》和《小时代 3》弹幕场开始，弹幕电影就成了个热闹电影。如今各个电影院推出弹幕场，你有兴趣围观，还是扭头就跑？", "record_count": 2433, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": null, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606161906nfEmsPLO1MDI6jHx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-08-11T10:37:28Z", "questions": [{"id": 55, "title": "弹幕电影突然火了，你有兴趣看吗？", "content": "弹幕电影突然火了，你有兴趣看吗？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 508, "content": "作为真正的弹幕粉，我觉得大银幕喷着更爽", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161729fuUwxmbhJ4kIpVad.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 509, "content": "不肯为这样的放映场花一分钱", "image": "img/option/option/2016060616172976ykizhp19x3j5du.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 510, "content": "这事儿需要体力，不可轻易尝试", "image": "img/option/option/201606061617292kQ9xmNR7jwoLK16.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 511, "content": "可以有机会让人在大银幕上跟我表白了", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161729r1d3JRyj2XSDVcls.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}